        <updateDate>2022-02-17T19:57:21Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Unmasking the Origins of COVID-19 Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of State to pay a reward for information leading to the identification of the origins of COVID-19 or other related information, such as the identification of individuals or entities involved in a cover-up of the origins of COVID-19.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
